!*             MSTopClose           to close the MS Addon part 
!*             MSTop_CheckLoadDLC	loads HPLCMS00.DLC
!*             LoadMacroMcxOrMac    to load an mcx-file (if it exists) otherwise
!*                                  the mac-file.
!*             MSOnlyConfigCheck    checks if the MSD is conf. as single module
!*             MSTop_LoadCPCom      to load HPCOM_01 and registers the CP-COM
!*                                  server in the ROT.           
!*************************************************************************************
